  "remarks": "LLC “NPO Aviabas” is a Russian company specialising in the manufacturing of unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs). It produces the Lun-7 and Lun-10 first-person view combat UAVs, which have been actively used by Russian forces in Ukraine for reconnaissance, strike and kamikaze missions. The company operates from St. Petersburg and plays a growing role in Russia’s expanding UAV warfare capabilities.",
